LOCUS       (OMMLV_pTI)_pTI_T7lacO_ 7187 bp ds-DNA     circular     30-MAR-2026
DEFINITION  .
COMMENT     OMMLV expression under pT7_Lac0 promoter (i.e. It has a Lac0 box to
            improve the promoter repression).  This system drives the
            expression of OMMLV in the presence of RNAT7 polymerase (which
            typically is induced by IPTG in E.coli BL21).
            Kanamycin Resistant
            pT7_Lac0::Riboj54_B0034::His_tag::GS_linker::OMMLV::3xStop::Tz in
            pTI
            tagged MMLV translation information:
            LacI and MMLV Sequences confirmed by sequencing
            Off-patent mutations:
            RNAse inactivation D524G/D853N/E562Q
            Thermostability V224M/D584N
            Processivity Q84A
            1) https://www.lens.org/lens/patent/US_4943531_A
            2) https://www.lens.org/lens/patent/077-031-766-454-504
            3) https://www.lens.org/lens/patent/092-167-377-902-293
            1) Expression of MMLV -first patent
            2) Loss of RNaseH activity
            3) Q84 mutation for increased processivity
